string-array.name: clockPriority_legend
string-array.item: Aggressive redraws every tick (Not recommended). Are you sure?
Aggressive redraws every minute, regardless of screen or launcher status. Are you sure?
Lazy redraws every minute when screen on, even when launcher is in background. Are you sure?
Lazy redraws every minute when launcher inactive or screen off. Are you sure?
No redraws when launcher inactive or screen off. Are you sure?

string-array.name: locationPriority_legend
string-array.item: Use only GPS location fixes less than 2 hours old. WARNING: Weather updates may stop if you are indoors. Are you sure?
Use network/GPS fixes less than 2 hours old. WARNING: Weather updates may stop if you are indoors. Are you sure?
Use only GPS location fixes less than 10 hours old. Weather updates may stop if you are indoors for more than 10 hours. Are you sure?
Use any network or GPS location less than 10 hours old. Weather updates may stop if you are indoors for more than 10 hours. Are you sure?
Use the most recent network or GPS location, regardless of staleness. Weather accuracy will depend on location accuracy and staleness. Are you sure?
